data.description: The price has been adjusted to reflect the current appraisal value. The seller is offering $5,000 towards concession at full price.    Classic Home with Modern Finishes! This beautifully renovated brick ranch has it all. Home has been completely taken down to the studs with new Electrical, HVAC, Plumbing, and Roof. Hardwood and tile floors throughout. Home features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Open concept living/dining with masonry fireplace. Separate master bedroom with masonry fireplace. Master and Secondary bedrooms feature vaulted ceilings and exposed beams. Custom kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Minutes to Serenbe and I-85, convenient to Hartsfield Jackson Airport and Atlanta.
